{
  "stem": "9168.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Question-- would you kindly stand up from your witness chair, take your earphones off, and proceed over to the defendant's dock and see if you can recognize the professor that you met at Dachau?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everyone in the courtroom waited tensely, just watching him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He stood up and then paused for just a moment with his eyes seemingly fixed on a doctor in the second row of the prisoner's dock.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then in a flash he was gone from the witness stand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He just seemed to be almost leaping over the ends of the German defense counsel's tables toward the prisoner's dock.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just almost appeared to be flying, with his right arm stretched high, reaching for Dr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Beiglboeck, the consulting physician to the German Air Force, the Luftwaffe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was instant-- we were all in kind of a state of shock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was confusion immediately in the courtroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And three of our American MPs who were standing behind the prisoner's dock rushed up in front and grabbed this little man almost in mid-air, who was just futilely bent on delivering his own brand of justice.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they subdued him just short of his target.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Moments later he stood before our distinguished chief judge of the four judge panel, Walter [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Biells ?] of Seattle, who sentenced him to 90 days in the Nuremberg prison for contempt of court.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Which was certainly kind of a shock to me, because I had already taken the testimony of all of this torture that he had undergone, to know that he was going to have to be sent to jail at that period-- for that period of time.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it took all of us a little bit of time to recover from that just momentarily.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
